&lt;b&gt;What steps will reproduce the problem?&lt;/b&gt;
1. You need a computer with Xp 32, NVIDIA GeForce 7600 GT, Driver Version: 6.14.0012.5721 (English) 
2. Setup Chrome on that computer so you can run NaCl webpages.
3. Open this page http://goo.gl/2BW4F
4. Start the second sample (Bump mapping)
5. Blue screen 

