Upgrading to the latest GeForce driver (Driver Version: 6.14.0012.8026 ) and it solve the blue screen, but the sample still runs very slow.

I guess we do something that GL doesn't like there, with the old driver you blue screen, with the new driver it is only slow...

I attached the dxdiag files of the computer with the old and new drivers.

Good luck with this issue. 

